<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<theme>
	<formatVersion>7</formatVersion>
	<view name="system">
		<image name="background1" extra="true">
			<storyboard>
				<animation property="pos" to="0.22 0.5" begin="2000" duration="1000" mode="linear"/>
			</storyboard>
		</image>
		<image name="background" extra="true">
			<zIndex>90</zIndex>
			<storyboard>
				<animation property="pos" to="1.5 0.5" begin="0" duration="0" mode="linear"/>
				<animation property="pos" to="0.95 0.5" begin="2000" duration="1000" mode="linear"/>
			</storyboard>
		</image>
		<video name="videobox" extra="true">
			<path>{random}</path>
			<path>./../../_inc/anim/video/${system.theme}.mp4</path>
			<path>./../../_inc/anim/video/${synonym}.mp4</path>
			<!-- Loads platform video from addon directory, if available -->
			<path>./../../../ckau-book-addons/_inc/anim/video/${system.theme}.mp4</path>
			<path>./../../../ckau-book-addons/_inc/anim/video/${synonym}.mp4</path>
			<default>./../../_inc/anim/video/CRT_Noise.mp4</default>
			<delay>0</delay>
			<effect>none</effect>
			<origin>0.5 0.5</origin>
			<origin if="${screen.ratio} == '4/3'">0.48 0.5</origin>
			<origin if="${screen.ratio} == '21/9'">0.535 0.5</origin>
			<pos>0.519 0.378</pos>
			<maxSize>0.27</maxSize>
			<zIndex>25</zIndex>
			<storyboard>
				<animation property="pos" to="0.239 0.378" begin="2000" duration="1000" mode="linear"/>
			</storyboard>
		</video>
		<text name="TextDate" extra="true">
			<pos>0.49 0.2</pos>
			<text/>
			<fontPath>./../../_inc/fonts/ubuntu_condensed.ttf</fontPath>
			<color>666666</color>
			<fontSize>0.03</fontSize>
			<zIndex>140</zIndex>
			<storyboard>
				<animation property="y" from="0.1" begin="3000" duration="1000" mode="linear"/>
				<animation property="opacity" to="0" begin="0" duration="0" mode="linear"/>
				<animation property="opacity" from="0" to="1" begin="3000" duration="1000" mode="EaseIn"/>
			</storyboard>
		</text>
		<text name="TextName" extra="true">
			<pos>0.49 0.25</pos>
			<size>0.5 0</size>
			<text>Lutro</text>
			<fontPath>./../../_inc/fonts/ubuntu_condensed.ttf</fontPath>
			<color>FFFFFF</color>
			<fontSize>0.065</fontSize>
			<lineSpacing>1.1</lineSpacing>
			<zIndex>140</zIndex>
			<storyboard>
				<animation property="x" from="0.5" begin="3000" duration="1000" mode="linear"/>
				<animation property="opacity" to="0" begin="0" duration="0" mode="linear"/>
				<animation property="opacity" from="0" to="1" begin="3000" duration="1000" mode="EaseIn"/>
			</storyboard>
		</text>
		<text name="TextDesc" extra="true">
			<size>0.5 0</size>
			<pos>0.49 0.35</pos>
			<text>Lutro is an experimental lua game framework that follows the LOVE API.
Lutro games can be played with LibRetro/RetroArch through the Lutro core.</text>
			<text lang="pl">Lutro jest eksperymentalnym frameworkiem gier lua, który podąża za LOVE API. Gry Lutro mogą być odtwarzane z LibRetro/RetroArch poprzez rdzeń Lutro.</text>
			<text lang="ru">Находящаяся в разработке повторная реализация Love 2D, написанная на Lua и реализованная как ядро Libretro. С Lutro можно легко создавать игры на Lua, не зная C или необходимости компилировать какой-либо код.</text>
			<text lang="es">Lutro es un framework experimental de juegos en lua que sigue la API LOVE.
Los juegos de Lutro se pueden jugar con LibRetro/RetroArch a través del núcleo de Lutro.</text>
			<text lang="de">Lutro ist ein experimentelles Lua-Spiel-Framework, das der LOVE-API folgt.
Lutro-Spiele können mit LibRetro/RetroArch über den Lutro-Kern gespielt werden.</text>
			<text lang="fr">Lutro est un cadre de jeu expérimental en Lua qui suit l'API LOVE.
Les jeux Lutro peuvent être joués avec LibRetro/RetroArch à travers le noyau Lutro.</text>
			<text lang="it">Lutro è un framework di gioco lua sperimentale che segue le API LOVE.
I giochi di Lutro possono essere giocati con LibRetro/RetroArch attraverso il core di Lutro.</text>
			<fontPath>./../../_inc/fonts/ubuntu_condensed.ttf</fontPath>
			<color>666666</color>
			<fontSize>0.025</fontSize>
			<lineSpacing>1.1</lineSpacing>
			<zIndex>140</zIndex>
			<storyboard>
				<animation property="y" from="0.8" begin="3000" duration="1000" mode="linear"/>
				<animation property="opacity" to="0" begin="0" duration="0" mode="linear"/>
				<animation property="opacity" from="0" to="1" begin="3000" duration="1000" mode="EaseIn"/>
			</storyboard>
		</text>
	</view>
</theme>
